# Brahmin Swarnkar

}}
Brahmin Swarnkar,Shrimali Swarnkar,Brahman Soni
The Brahmin Swarnkar are an Indian caste of Shrimali Brahmans, which developed from Shrimal Nagar (now known as Bhinmal). A group of Brahmins adopted a Swarnkar business for their enhancement of life style, and so these Brahmins are called as "Brahmin Swarnkars". Swarnkars are mainly found in local areas of Rajasthan like Barmer,Jaisalmer,Jodhpur,Etc. Rajasthan.
